data.description: 3- Bedroom 1- Bath home Fresh paint inside and outside. Semi private location. Metal Roof, Central Air/ Heat Pump 16x32 In ground pool with a brand new liner. Pool has a chain link fence around it .Move in ready. Fresh Gravel on the driveway. Covered front porch to enjoy the fall air. Pool is covered but it will be ready to enjoy this summer. Also has a detached 18x20 metal carport and 10x16 storage building. All kitchen appliances included .New Flooring in most of the home. Large laundry room. Get ready to entertain this coming summer with family and friends!!!
